# Clean Code Principles

Defer to **code-standard.mdc**, **generic.mdc**, **performance-architecture-standards.mdc**.

Principles: names intention-revealing; functions small, 0–2 args; comments only "why"; DRY; prefer component maps for conditionals (code-standard.mdc § Conditional Rendering).
